{"tid":469104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡地鐵追撞 23人傷","createTime":"2017-11-15T04:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:43:57.000Z","uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9228b1f4d22c7298345a8c4f5c50082e445673b7","tid":469104,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"SMRT地鐵發生追尾事故 23人受傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/201711/20171115/mrt215112017.jpg?itok=wOM_zQOi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Farticle_large_full%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F201711%2F20171115%2Fmrt215112017.jpg%3Fitok%3DwOM_zQOi&h=82acc921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一輛列車在裕群站附近撞上另一輛停在軌道上的列車，23名乘客受傷入院。（圖／MEI ANNE面簿）<br />\n<br />\nSMRT地鐵發生追尾相撞事故，一輛列車在裕群站附近撞上另一輛停在軌道上的列車，23名乘客受傷入院。<br />\n<br />\n這起事故發生在今早8時許。<br />\n<br />\n民防部隊在10時42分發表面簿貼文說，今早8時33分接到通報指，裕群站附近發生事故，民防人員正在現場為傷者提供援助。目前，已有23名乘客送院治療，大部分人只受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/realtime/singapore/story20171115-811179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Frealtime%2Fsingapore%2Fstory20171115-811179&d=wbblXAdUUDw7h6ZmuthJ0F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ecec3ab7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zaobao.com/realtime/singapore/story20171115-811179</a>"},{"pid":"85341a1872281ef8773a768520bab609ab5f807d","tid":469104,"uid":157292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126381abce4207f4ed37d1926ddf23fd776d6561","tid":469104,"uid":129209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"SMRT好過MTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出嚟回應下"},{"pid":"b4236be4465122622d009f8e731c74699373cf3d","tid":469104,"uid":5542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"呢d事會係發達城市發生？ 要錯幾多樣野？"},{"pid":"f8cfb72a3990e144c4c3d65437012648fc40e237","tid":469104,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SMRT好過MTR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出嚟回應下</blockquote><br />\n文毒呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3271065bdbcafb0e2a27a5714d8e9c283c5d216","tid":469104,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"又係支那"},{"pid":"cf6b7e8ebaeb7a0ec685d292b7bcc85a0159aa7a","tid":469104,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係支那</blockquote><br />\n信號應該係Westinghouse <br />\n架車唔肯定係川重定川重+南車"},{"pid":"3009edacfe25e06908960b6b8a32a73d77508bd1","tid":469104,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:43:57.000Z","msg":"乘客問題"}]}